{"tid":1775722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍵盤戰士唔應該停留喺低成本抗爭","createTime":"2019-12-09T04:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T17:18:48.000Z","uid":71237,"like":157,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"a6151d1584d7c6b09e7895692cd4adac0d509a29","tid":1775722,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士唔應該停留喺低成本抗爭<br />\n<br />\n依半年大家曾經發展過好多條鍵盤戰線，令人印象深刻嘅包括白宮聯署、Twitter戰線。<br />\n唔少參加者都抱住「低成本」的心態參與，認為只係花幾分鐘按個制，佢地最鍾意話「無成本點解唔做？」「唔做又點知有冇用？」<br />\n做一件事應該係因為有用，而唔係因為無成本。<br />\n祈禱夠低成本啦，你有冇早晚祈禱，求天主叫林鄭月娥釋放義士呀？你唔祈禱又點知祈禱冇用呀？<br />\n<br />\n坦白講，成本低又簡單嘅抗爭手法很可能代表無用。<br />\n我喺連登見過好多post呼籲大家去傳媒Facebook page同人地鬥多like、去警察Facebook page比嬲嬲、去藍絲YouTube channel比dislike。坦白講我覺得依啲行為只係浪費自己人時間。<br />\n<br />\n要真係造出貢獻，唔可以淨係靠求其click幾下。<br />\n鍵盤戰士本身被捕風險已經比勇武低。人地為你地擋緊子彈，你坐喺電腦面前專登揀搵成本最低的方法，求其click幾下就覺得自己做咗嘢，其實唔配稱為「戰士」。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n以下列舉一些我認為用途不大的低成本手法：<br />\n- 白宮聯署、<a href=\"http://change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchange.org&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=86e68f09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">change.org</a>聯署<br />\n- 集體去藍絲Facebook page、藍絲YouTube比嬲嬲或者dislike<br />\n- 用template send一模一樣嘅投訴信去公營機構<br />\n- 參與傳媒搞嘅網上投票<br />\n- 入藍絲的fb group鬧幾句然後秒速被ban<br />\n<br />\n鍵盤戰士唔可以淨係揀最低成本的方法，當目前的方法無效，應該思考如何提高成效。<br />\n哨兵tg group嘅admin我覺得係完美的鍵盤戰士。長時間幫大家整合資訊嘅成本一定好高，但作用亦都好大。<br />\n專業精算師踢爆何君堯祖墳越界、舉報藍絲店舖違法僭建圍板、投訴藍絲食肆亦都威力驚人。背後亦需要專業知識，大量時間心血去做。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n唔係每一個人都有能力做專業精算師，但係只要你肯用心去諗，一定有比聯署、Facebook比嬲嬲更好嘅事可以做。如果你乜都諗唔到，我情願你唔好做鍵盤戰士，落街做哨兵好過，或者搵下啲區議員睇下佢地收唔收義工。<br />\n<br />\n鍵盤戰士可以做嘅事：<br />\n- 玩Twitter戰線嘅唔好淨係share一模一樣嘅post，要嘗試同外國人交流，解釋香港的情況，回應對方的疑問。<br />\n- 玩維基百科嘅，唔好搞小學雞式破壞，要認真學習維基百科的方針。<br />\n- 喺屋企睇直播嘅，唔好淨係得個睇字。可以同步記錄並報告警方動態，或者backup你睇到嘅影片。<br />\n- 成日上Facebook嘅，唔好淨係like + share完就算，嘗試將你睇到嘅優質文章、圖片做有系統嘅整理。<br />\n- 得閒嘅可以協助整理唔同行業的黃店list<br />\n- 擅長反駁嘅亦都可以去「反駁藍絲資料庫」寫嘢<br />\n- 滲入咗藍絲group嘅可以搞一大堆聯署、投票去浪費藍絲的時間，亦可以用「低級紅、高級黑」去暗中搞破壞<br />\n- 大家諗到其他歡迎提出<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n術業有專攻，如果你玩Twitter好叻嘅，你就應該專心玩Twitter，唔好分心喺太多唔同project。分心只會減弱你喺Twitter的威力。同埋你應該分享經驗，教其他人點樣可以玩到同你一樣咁叻。<br />\n<br />\n大家亦可以諗下點樣同其他人協作。<br />\n我記得幾年前出現過一個apps整理立法會議員的投票記錄，但係隔咗幾年就停止運作。如果整個計劃係以協作的方式進行，原作者想休息就唔會令成個計劃中止。希望大家開始一個project之前，應該諗下依個project係咪只係靠你一個人去maintain，同埋如果你唔想再maintain落去，應該點樣交棒比其他人。<br />\n<br />\n協作亦都可以令你個project做得更好。例如你係backup師，想backup直播新聞片段。最簡單係可以自己backup完放喺Google drive比其他人download。<br />\n問題係你整完都無渠道傳播出去，而且有朝一日你唔想做落去，成個project就無以為繼。而且很可能一早有人做緊類似的工作，如果你做得唔夠人地好，最後你的心血可能就白費。<br />\n<br />\n比較好嘅做法係聯絡其他backup師，傾一個比較好嘅backup方法。同時容許其他人幫backup咗嘅影片、相片加hashtag，方便其他人檢索。加hashtag的工作可以交比其他唔識IT嘅鍵盤戰士去做。"},{"pid":"3a47c2b53529e7fc2da7a57a945de480295208df","tid":1775722,"uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:40:35.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀：<br />\n反駁藍絲資料庫成立40日，大家估下有幾多人睇過？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1767005/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1767005/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[教學] 如何成為維基百科撰寫師？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n一班人去維基百科集體投票保留配音員條目，結果全部被ban<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1774169/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1774169/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈最需要嘅唔係創意，而係各行各業的黃店list<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1760146/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1760146/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n發現藍絲的telegram/whatsapp群組，唔應該入去罵戰洗版。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1554564/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1554564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n對抗FB/IG/YouTube五毛的最佳做法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1481603/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1481603/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n好多人以為FB比嬲嬲或者YouTube比Dislike就可以令對家收皮<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1393582/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1393582/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n「無成本，點解唔做？」好多人都誤解咗成本的概念。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1565102/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1565102/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n最新白宮聯署出爐！！誓要黑警永世留喺大灣區！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1661597/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1661597/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n有咩on9得過集體自首等警察處理唔切 / 迫爆監倉？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436334/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436334/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"517fd6d4536b8968865a19a20602bf8e0f09135c","tid":1775722,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:41:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17ff1b15485e2f0afbfa55ed17fee8afe45d6ec4","tid":1775722,"uid":223468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26842efc431dbf05082d9d4dcda89986daf73e89","tid":1775722,"uid":54708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b22cee1230c3ef78ecc33d2d2f119b67c5c3b4","tid":1775722,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:44:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44d635df9be630a3d0e3bf20935e55781a794c37","tid":1775722,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"我依個post係針對鍵盤戰士講嘅。<br />\n<br />\n你地做鍵盤戰士本身已經比上街嘅人更安全，應該盡力諗下點樣做多啲，而唔係諗點樣最輕鬆簡單。"},{"pid":"40fe253709455e62d76a10dabb82eb393f1c4ee3","tid":1775722,"uid":93383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:49:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4f48a5e612e0227be1926f636e50e8f3441b4258","tid":1775722,"uid":180370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:51:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01137487c015b262703dc304e31029aba918d096","tid":1775722,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:51:21.000Z","msg":"對唔住🙇🏻&zwj;♂️，借個位宣傳一下：<br />\n<br />\n和你開工會：七人成團，重光勞工界，只剩唔夠四個月！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1775618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1775618</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d46a002003f32bae3c79f18a3b689edce43e5758","tid":1775722,"uid":84614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c37550344b4697355fa6891d0cbc88de34790a","tid":1775722,"uid":89663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:53:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"756cd2e469458853c7c3e06b4ee6a99dd3d1fa5b","tid":1775722,"uid":37234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:54:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b32058dd633896c66697556142ba8d4e4d36e309","tid":1775722,"uid":117282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91323094677f04b83e9087f72b11409cbd543efe","tid":1775722,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"如果你係某樣嘢嘅專家，你應該 1. 教其他人變到同你一樣咁叻 2. 諗下其他人有咩可以幫到你，令你可以專注做你最擅長嘅嘢。"},{"pid":"15501cd0f235c7953cce2e879276441217db3d9e","tid":1775722,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:01:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"531d5741cc18d9be56dec6833c6145db48ec28b3","tid":1775722,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"89a1d58df2da330adf6af2abca7226152d3068ef","tid":1775722,"uid":71237,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"見到藍絲page, Youtube貼fake news<br />\n應該report而唔係dislike"},{"pid":"292fc5efe2aa6e7f78a1086d6d8a45e8bbfe7afb","tid":1775722,"uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"發現藍絲whatsapp群組，唔應該入去大叫光復香港時代革命，然後秒速被踢。<br />\n<br />\n你可以套取對方個人資料，引導對方去做浪費時間又無用嘅事，掌握對家流傳緊咩fake news，用低級紅高級黑令佢地思想混亂。"},{"pid":"f476577a1b17a44e9e6f19ec80e46f37ad6ddfa8","tid":1775722,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"有樣野我覺得都好重要<br />\n有深藍家庭唔代表要反面<br />\n扮下野，唔好一黎就做深黃反面<br />\n做個中間派<br />\n諗下計點樣拉佢地去做中間派<br />\n先再去諗點拉佢地做黃<br />\n<br />\n成日覺得好冇力既人<br />\n其實你身邊都有好多戰線<br />\n包括你朋友、屋企人、親戚、公司<br />\n唔好俾連登規範咗自己只可以出黎做大型抗爭"},{"pid":"be6567a3dccbce8c8b5066a8a654f09bd57d9611","tid":1775722,"uid":200532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"outliers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefce46fd86ce4eb971282db215b5d3cb53cea73","tid":1775722,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"你死啦"},{"pid":"6bdf8ae77d09765fef99dd1e247bf97a17f4bafe","tid":1775722,"uid":6752,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"講真話好難聽架<br />\n等收負皮"},{"pid":"93035e03cbdd9e3f1ddeea3db42257bde320ebd4","tid":1775722,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be6567a3dccbce8c8b5066a8a654f09bd57d9611","tid":1775722,"uid":200532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"outliers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919122b99064b4dc589145615745bd7ccde047d8","tid":1775722,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"88518ea4233b3f6fcc892f91417544ab36327d13","tid":1775722,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim